{"type":"message","id":"6d355d10","parentId":"a277bf7a","timestamp":"2026-04-14T13:50:13.281Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了！在 `~/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions` 目录下发现了 **7 处** 包含 `\"stopReason\":\"error\"` 的记录，都发生在 `.reset.*` 类型的文件中：\n\n**错误原因统一为：**\n`400 'max_tokens' or 'max_completion_tokens' is too large: 16384. This model's maximum context length is 65536 tokens and your request has XXXXX input tokens (16384 > 65536 - XXXXX).`\n\n**涉及的文件：**\n1. `7b971aed-e825-456c-a609-bdb2463e6ccc.jsonl.reset.2026-04-13T07-46-28.872Z` - 输入 token: 54129\n2. `eb05b9da-88b1-4e96-8e91-5bab2fdeb854.jsonl.reset.2026-04-14T13-43-54.534Z` - 2 处错误，输入 token: 59325 和 59431\n3. `46ab4208-374c-4215-853c-5c7987c2e791.jsonl.reset.2026-04-13T07-49-48.941Z` - 输入 token: 57458\n4. `44b23a7e-471e-4d06-b7d3-9c354e67b2f9.jsonl.reset.2026-04-13T07-43-22.366Z` - 2 处错误，输入 token: 54128 和 54307\n5. `c4803ea6-54cc-4d56-a500-bc98653190ca.jsonl.reset.2026-04-14T13-49-35.396Z` - 输入 token: 50183（这是刚才的会话）\n\n**问题根源：** 请求的 `max_tokens` 设置为 16384，但输入 token 数已经接近或超过模型的 65536 token 上限，导致剩余空间不足以生成 16384 个 token。\n\n需要调整 `max_tokens` 参数或者清理上下文来避免这个错误。需要我帮你详细分析某个特定会话吗？🦞"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"my-qwen-provider","model":"AIAPLLM-vision-nothink","usage":{"input":21165,"output":620,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21785,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776174604256,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9a94d93b-c525-4679-ada0-c7a24d53fcc9"}}
